title: Spiral Doubles Down. SAW Sequel Moves Up Release!
author: Reel Talk
comment: i was honestly not expecting for it to keep its release, let alone push up the date!!! I’m so happy 🥺💓
Going to theaters for this one.
If JIGSAW grossed $100 million worldwide and that wasnt “enough” then there is no realistic future for this franchise, theatrically.
Theatres! We have had them open here in Australia since July 2020 and now they're back to full capacity.
I HOPE Spiral is very successful 🙏 I really want more SAW sequels!
description:
Spiral Doubles Down. SAW Sequel Moves Up Release! With big movies running for safer ground, Spiral From the Book of SAW has not only confirmed that it will be a theater only experience, but it moved up its release date. Is this a good move? Let's talk!
